import pyautogui
import time

try:
    # Press Win key to open Start menu
    pyautogui.press('win')
    time.sleep(0.5)
    # Type 'notepad' to search
    pyautogui.write('notepad', interval=0.05)
    time.sleep(0.5)
    # Press Enter to launch Notepad
    pyautogui.press('enter')
    time.sleep(1)
    # Verify Notepad window exists
    if pyautogui.getWindowsWithTitle('Notepad'):
        print("EXECUTION_SUCCESS")
    else:
        print("FAILED: Notepad window not found")
except Exception as e:
    print(f"FAILED: {e}")
